name: I am not your type, harvester
name_original: I am not your type, harvester
description:
| Ludum Dare |

The game was made in very few hours. Less than 12. I had a few ideas in mind; I might make this concept a lot more vivid in the future.

Careful if you have carpal tunnel with this game; it's a bit tough on the hands.

|Vote of Thanks|

I thank my creator for helping me through this project. It was a lot of fun.
